title: Toronto Blue Jays-Kansas City Royals in ALCS Game 1: Start time, what TV channel, how to watch live stream online
text:
The Toronto Blue Jays and Kansas City Royals open the best-of-seven American League Championship Series with Friday's Game 1 in Kansas City. Here are the details:
What : Toronto Blue Jays at Kansas City Royals in ALCS Game 1
Where : Kauffman Stadium, Kansas City
When : Friday, October 16, at 5:07 p.m. PT/8:07 p.m. ET
What TV channel : TV on Fox, radio on KMTT (910 AM) in Portland area
Live updates : Follow along in the comments section below for live updates during the game
Watch and listen online : Watch online at Fox Sports Go . Listen at ESPNRadio.com .
Pitching matchup : Toronto's Marco Estrada vs. Kansas City's Edinson Volquez
Playoff schedule : Bookmark our MLB scoreboard for postseason scores and schedules.
